title: Harry Fraud x The Internet - "Better Liar" (OFFICIAL AUDIO STREAM)
description:
"Better Liar," from Harry Fraud and The Internet, is the third track on the Converse compilation CONS EP VOL. 1. The track was recorded at Capitol Studios in Los Angeles, California.

Produced by: Harry Fraud 
Music by: Harry Fraud and The Internet 
Lyrics by: The Internet
Vocals by: The Internet
